```plantuml
@startuml UBC-CIC_Student-Connect-App

actor User
participant "React PWA" as PWA
participant "AWS Cognito" as Auth
participant "GraphQL API" as API
participant "Lambda Function" as Lambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DB
participant "Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "DynamoDB Stream" as Stream

User -> PWA: Access Application
PWA -> Auth: Sign-In/Sign-Up
Auth -> PWA: Authentication Token

PWA -> API: Fetch User Preferences
API -> DB: Query User Preferences
DB -> API: Return Preferences
API -> PWA: Return Preferences

PWA -> API: Fetch Data
API -> Lambda: Trigger Data Fetch
Lambda -> DB: Fetch Data from External Sources
DB -> DB: Store Data
DB -> Lambda: Return Data

Lambda -> ES: Update ES Index
ES -> Lambda: Acknowledge Update

PWA -> API: Query for Recommendations
API -> ES: Query Documents for User Interests
ES -> API: Return Documents
API -> PWA: Return Recommendations

Stream -> Lambda: Trigger on Data Change
Lambda -> ES: Sync ES with DB
ES -> Lambda: Confirm Sync

PWA -> User: Display Personalized Content

@enduml
```